코드 전체를 보니 문제가 명확해졌어요. 기존 소스 기준으로 수정할게요.

---

## 발견된 문제

### 1. `fireParticipants` — Extension Point 조회 방식 오류 (핵심)

```java
// ❌ 현재 - 두 개 인자 버전: "bxm.ui" 플러그인 안의 "bxm.team.scm.git.commit" 를 찾음
// → 실제 full ID가 "bxm.ui.bxm.team.scm.git.commit" 이 되어버려서 null 반환
IExtensionPoint ep = registry.getExtensionPoint("bxm.ui", "bxm.team.scm.git.commit");

// ✅ 수정 - 단일 인자 버전: SVN이 point="bxm.team.scm.svn.commit" 으로 동작하는 것과 동일한 방식
IExtensionPoint ep = registry.getExtensionPoint("bxm.team.scm.git.commit");
```

### 2. `prepareTreeParser` — ObjectReader 리소스 누수

```java
// ❌ 현재 - RevWalk만 닫히고 ObjectReader는 안 닫힘
try (org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevWalk walk = new org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevWalk(repo)) {
    org.eclipse.jgit.lib.ObjectReader reader = repo.newObjectReader(); // 누수!

// ✅ 수정
try (org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevWalk walk = new org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevWalk(repo);
     org.eclipse.jgit.lib.ObjectReader reader = repo.newObjectReader()) {
```

---

## 수정된 전체 코드

### `BxmGitRepositoryInitializer.java`

```java
package bxm.team.scm.git;

import java.io.File;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.Comparator;
import java.util.List;

import org.eclipse.core.runtime.CoreException;
import org.eclipse.core.runtime.IConfigurationElement;
import org.eclipse.core.runtime.IExtension;
import org.eclipse.core.runtime.IExtensionPoint;
import org.eclipse.core.runtime.IExtensionRegistry;
import org.eclipse.core.runtime.Platform;
import org.eclipse.jgit.api.Git;
import org.eclipse.jgit.diff.DiffEntry;
import org.eclipse.jgit.lib.ObjectReader;
import org.eclipse.jgit.lib.Repository;
import org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevCommit;
import org.eclipse.jgit.revwalk.RevWalk;
import org.eclipse.jgit.treewalk.AbstractTreeIterator;
import org.eclipse.jgit.treewalk.CanonicalTreeParser;

public class BxmGitRepositoryInitializer {

    public void init(Repository repo) {
        // addRefsChangedListener — 기존 방식 유지
        repo.getListenerList().addRefsChangedListener(event -> {
            try (Git git = new Git(repo)) {
                RevCommit latest = git.log().setMaxCount(1).call().iterator().next();
                List<String> files = getChangedFiles(git, repo, latest);
                fireParticipants(files, repo.getWorkTree());
            } catch (Exception e) {
                e.printStackTrace();
            }
        });
    }

    private List<String> getChangedFiles(Git git, Repository repo, RevCommit commit) throws Exception {
        List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
        if (commit.getParentCount() == 0) return result;

        RevCommit parent = commit.getParent(0);
        List<DiffEntry> diffs = git.diff()
                .setOldTree(prepareTreeParser(repo, parent))
                .setNewTree(prepareTreeParser(repo, commit))
                .call();

        for (DiffEntry diff : diffs) {
            switch (diff.getChangeType()) {
                case ADD:    result.add("A:" + diff.getNewPath()); break;
                case MODIFY: result.add("M:" + diff.getNewPath()); break;
                case DELETE: result.add("D:" + diff.getOldPath()); break;
                default: break;
            }
        }
        return result;
    }

    private void fireParticipants(List<String> files, File repoRoot) {
        IExtensionRegistry registry = Platform.getExtensionRegistry();

        // ✅ 단일 인자로 변경 — SVN과 동일한 방식
        IExtensionPoint ep = registry.getExtensionPoint("bxm.team.scm.git.commit");
        if (ep == null) {
            System.err.println("[BXM] Extension point 'bxm.team.scm.git.commit' not found");
            return;
        }

        List<IBxmGitCommitParticipant> participants = new ArrayList<>();
        for (IExtension ext : ep.getExtensions()) {
            for (IConfigurationElement el : ext.getConfigurationElements()) {
                try {
                    IBxmGitCommitParticipant p =
                        (IBxmGitCommitParticipant) el.createExecutableExtension("class");
                    participants.add(p);
                } catch (CoreException e) {
                    e.printStackTrace();
                }
            }
        }

        participants.sort(Comparator.comparingInt(IBxmGitCommitParticipant::getPriority));
        for (IBxmGitCommitParticipant p : participants) {
            Object pre = p.performPreProcess();
            p.performAfterCommitTasks(pre, files, repoRoot);
            p.performPostProcess();
        }
    }

    private AbstractTreeIterator prepareTreeParser(Repository repo, RevCommit commit) throws Exception {
        // ✅ ObjectReader도 try-with-resources로 닫기
        try (RevWalk walk = new RevWalk(repo);
             ObjectReader reader = repo.newObjectReader()) {
            CanonicalTreeParser parser = new CanonicalTreeParser();
            parser.reset(reader, walk.parseTree(commit.getTree()));
            return parser;
        }
    }
}
```

### `BxmGitRepositoryManager.java` — `job.schedule()` 및 리스너 주석 해제

```java
public void start() {
    RepositoryUtil repoUtil = RepositoryUtil.INSTANCE;

    // 기존 저장소 등록
    repoUtil.getRepositories().forEach(this::register);

    // ✅ 주석 해제 — 신규 저장소도 감지
    repoUtil.addPropertyChangeListener(event -> {
        if (RepositoryUtil.REPOSITORIES_CHANGED.equals(event.getProperty())) {
            repoUtil.getRepositories().forEach(this::register);
        }
    });
}
```

### `BxmGitRepositoryInit.java` — `job.schedule()` 추가

```java
@Override
public void earlyStartup() {
    Job job = new Job("BXM Git") {
        @Override
        protected IStatus run(IProgressMonitor monitor) {
            new BxmGitRepositoryManager().start();
            return Status.OK_STATUS;
        }
    };
    job.schedule(); // ✅ 누락되어 있었음
}
```

---

## 변경 요약

| 위치 | 문제 | 수정 |
|---|---|---|
| `fireParticipants` | `getExtensionPoint("bxm.ui", ...)` → null 반환 | 단일 인자 `getExtensionPoint("bxm.team.scm.git.commit")` |
| `prepareTreeParser` | `ObjectReader` 리소스 누수 | try-with-resources에 추가 |
| `BxmGitRepositoryManager.start()` | 신규 저장소 감지 안 됨 | `PropertyChangeListener` 주석 해제 |
| `BxmGitRepositoryInit.earlyStartup()` | Job이 실행 안 됨 | `job.schedule()` 추가 |
